

#### What is MSFVENOM? ####

- Metasploit framework used to generate, encode, and customize payloads


#### What is the purpose of Encoders? ####

- Encoders are meant to obfsucate the signature of the payload.

    - They put the shell code into a different format to avoid Anti-Virus(AV) detection.
        - They alter signature patterns, remove "bad characters" (e.g., null bytes \x00) that can break exploits, 
        and ensure payload stability.

